headline: Looking At The Narrative For L3Harris Technologies After Missile Spinout And Department Of War Deal
summary: The fair value estimate for L3Harris Technologies has been raised from about US$364 to roughly US$380.63, with updated modeling also reflecting slightly different assumptions for revenue growth and discount rate. Street research has reacted to the planned spinout of the Missile Solutions business and the planned US$1b preferred equity investment from the Department of War, which together are feeding into refreshed views on what the stock could be worth.
